        <h3>2. How can I ensure my meal is gluten-free?</h3>
        <p>Communicate your dietary needs to the server and ask about cross-contamination practices. Many restaurants have dedicated gluten-free menus or can modify dishes to meet your requirements.</p>

        <h3>3. Are there dedicated gluten-free restaurants in the area?</h3>
        <p>While there are no exclusively gluten-free restaurants, many establishments offer a wide range of gluten-free options and take extra precautions to ensure safety.</p>

